{"about_the_game":"Retro Rally! is a top-down racing game where classic arcade racing meets modern excitement. Race head-to-head in local co-op Circuit Mode or test your speed in challenging time trials. Championship races and a high-stakes Gauntlet Mode await. Get ready for a nostalgic, adrenaline-pumping journey back to classic arcade gaming.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669620/extras/farm_tornado_yeet_small_short_.gif?t=1739595389\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Local Multiplayer</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Up to 4 player local multiplayer<br></li><li> Race head-to-head in circuit mode</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669620/extras/cemetery_short_gif_medium.gif?t=1739595389\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Circuit Mode</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 4 standard circuits<br></li><li> 4 unlock-able reverse circuits<br></li><li> Supports 4 player local multiplayer or single player vs 3 AI</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669620/extras/circuit-mode-550px.jpg?t=1739595389\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Time Trial Mode</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 16 tracks<br></li><li> 16 unlock-able reverse tracks<br></li><li> Bronze, silver and gold medal challenge times</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gauntlet Mode</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Standard gauntlet mode (cycles the normal tracks)<br></li><li> Random gauntlet mode (randomizes the track order)<br></li><li> Race until you lose (AI increases in difficulty as you progress)<br></li><li> Collect money and upgrade your car to keep up!<br></li><li> Rack up a high score with money and race time bonuses</li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2669620?t=1739595389","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2669620?t=1739595389","capsule_image":"https